text: Bhai kele tuj jaisa tu akela hi hai. Pehli baar stage pe jab tere first words sune tabse hi laga ki yeh bhai alag hai. Kabhi socha nai tha ki apna group same hoga. But humara common point bohot strong tha..yes u guessed it right FRAUD MAARNA (lol) but srsly aage bhi hope hai ki tu aise hi chaapte rahega. All the best bro. And MA.KU.NA.HA is forever so ofc we all will meet soon
author: Kush Shailesh Bagla

text: As per our bet I am forced to write this. Thanks for helping me out these years with all the projects and stuff. Also mentor wali baat pe I have no comments.
author: Kush Shailesh Bagla

text: South and North Pole hai apan dono. Kaun hi socha honga Roomies honge for 2 whole years. Tu sala over active insaan aur mai pura din sone wala. phir bhi apni tuning ka kya hi kehna. Mai tere memoir me sirf issliye likhra hu taki clg walo ko pata chale ki Kush naam ka bhi launda tha jo Ujjjwal(wont miss the 3 j's) ka roomie tha. warna tere liye jo kehna hai woh toh mai direct bhi keh hi sakta hu. So jab bhi yeh padhega ek call kar lena meko mast gappe marenge baithke. and plz mera room me rakha saaman sambhal lena lol...
author: Kush Shailesh Bagla

text: oye chappu mote(ab mota bhi nai bol sakta teko). Tu nai hota toh mai first year me hi latak jata lol. Tere bina toh soch bhi nai sakta ki iitk me kya haal hua rehta. tu sale baapu se kam nai tha mere liye. thanks bhai 4 saal sehne k liye meko. But let me tell u something ab aur 40 jhelna padega kyoki mai jaha bhi jaunga teko tang jarur karunga lol. Hope to meet u soon and memoir sirf natak hai asli rona call pe sunaunga hehe
author: Kush Shailesh Bagla
